      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLAZING PRINCE (1) hasn't been far away, finishing in the money twice in a row including last time in a Grade 5 at this track over 515m. Good beginner and aided by the inside draw. Better than last run and makes appeal this time. FEDERAL FELIX (8) has been hard to follow lately, running seventh (30.52) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Gosford. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Well placed here and can atone this time. KAREN STRATUS (2) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive before that in her strong 22.90 win at this track over 400m. Expecting another bold showing. SAIL AWAY SAM (6) is a last-start placegetter worth considering.",
